{
    "poem_title": "- LIV - ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Francisco de La Torre",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Ay, no te alejes, Filis, ay, espera",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "el tu Damón que más que a su ganado",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "te reverencia y ama, y si el osado",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "curso prosigues, tiembla la carrera.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ay, no te alejes, Filis, ay, espera\nel tu Damón que más que a su ganado\nte reverencia y ama, y si el osado\ncurso prosigues, tiembla la carrera."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Ya no te sigo, Filis, la ligera",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "plata refrena, que el temor helado",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "de tu mal me detiene, y tú el amado",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "Damón huyes cruel, cual cruda fiera.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++--+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ya no te sigo, Filis, la ligera\nplata refrena, que el temor helado\nde tu mal me detiene, y tú el amado\nDamón huyes cruel, cual cruda fiera."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Detén, Filis, cruel, detén el paso;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "no te ofenda la planta riguroso",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "cardo cruel de tierra no labrada.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Detén, Filis, cruel, detén el paso;\nno te ofenda la planta riguroso\ncardo cruel de tierra no labrada."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "Diciendo aquesto triste y doloroso,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "esquivando la vida desdichada,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "cayó Damón al Sol del campo raso.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Diciendo aquesto triste y doloroso,\nesquivando la vida desdichada,\ncayó Damón al Sol del campo raso."
        }
    ]
}